Hardware Requirements:

1. Arduino: Arduino 33 BLE Sense
2. Android phone: Running android version 8 or above

Installation instructions:

To install arduino code:

1. Open the fitbit.ino in arduino IDE.
2. Set the board to Arduino Nano 33 BLE sense.
3. Flash the arduino with the source code.

To install companion app:

1. Open FitBitAndroidApp in Android Studio.
2. Connect your android phone to computer.
3. Click install and run on Android studio.